          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">The price per kg of sweetcorn is considered for the years 2016-2021 for the state of Florida in the US. The values were retrieved in $/CWT [1] and converted into $/kg. References: [1] US Department of Agriculture (NASS), Quickstat, TabLe "SWEETCORN - PRICE RECEIVED, MEASURED IN $ / CWT", accessed on 25.08.2023, available at: https://quickstats.nass.usda.gov/
The prices were converted to EUR based on the annual exchange rates published by the European Central Bank (https://sdw.ecb.europa.eu/quickview.do?SERIES_KEY=120.EXR.A.AUD.EUR.SP00.A, last accessed on 2023-06-01) and adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 using the producer price index (PPI) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/STS_INPP_A__custom_6416181/default/table?lang=en, last accessed on 2023-06-01).</comment>
        </property>
